                            independent professional appointed by the company's board of directors.
                        </p>
                        <p class="wow animate__animated animate__fadeInUp pb-2" data-wow-delay="0.8s">At Deepwork, we
                            have cost auditor professionals who examine the cost accounting records and reports prepared
                            by the company to ensure compliance with the relevant laws and regulations. The auditor also
                            checks for any discrepancies or errors in the records and reports.
                            <br><br>
                            The purpose of cost and works compliance is to ensure that companies maintain accurate and
                            reliable cost accounting records and reports, which help in effective decision-making and
                            efficient management of resources. Compliance also helps to prevent fraud and mismanagement
                            of funds, thereby safeguarding the interests of shareholders and other stakeholders.
                        </p>
